data.description: LOCATION, LARGE OPEN CONCEPT FLOOR PLAN, LOFT, GUEST BEDROOM, are just a few of the amazing features that this home has to offer! This is the home of your dreams, featuring 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms! The guest bedroom is located on the 1st floor and has a separate bathroom entrance! The large kitchen is the perfect spot to host any gathering just in time for the Holidays! Upstairs you will find the 4 bedrooms, laundry room, loft space! The owners suite offers large walk in closet, his and her vanities, beautifully tiled shower! All rooms are very spacious and offer ceiling fans in each room ! Don't miss the opportunity to live in this amazing neighborhood! Easy commute to BMW, Greenville-Spartanburg International Airport and Greenville!
